reviewText: ok, but not what I really expected.
An excellent resource for my classroom. My students love it.

I cannot rate this product since I have been waiting over a month to get the product.  If I do not recieve the item by this Friday and I am going to request that my credit card company credit back by account.  I would have never order from this copmpany if I realized it woud take over a month to get my item.
This was a great addition when my daughter had to write and create a speech on Harriet Tubman.  Watching the DVD and reading the books gave her what she needed to do an A+ job on her report.
